  calories: 630 kcal
  fat: 26 g
  saturated fat: 10 g
  carbohydrates: 55 g
  sugar: 6 g
  protein: 40 g
  fiber: 2 g
  sodium: 600 mg
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/ginger-soy-chicken-and-bell-pepper-5cf144d003169c001a78381d
servings: 2
